<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تُكَذِّبانِ تجحدان أيها الثقلان.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>[سورة الرحمن <span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> : الآيات ٧٦ الى ٧٨]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُتَّكِئِينَ عَلى رَفْرَفٍ خُضْرٍ وَعَبْقَرِيٍّ حِسانٍ <span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> فَبِأَيِّ آلاءِ رَبِّكُما تُكَذِّبانِ <span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> تَبارَكَ اسْمُ رَبِّكَ ذِي الْجَلالِ وَالْإِكْرامِ <span class="c2">(٧٨)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧٦-<span class="c5"> مُتَّكِئِينَ عَلى رَفْرَفٍ خُضْرٍ وَعَبْقَرِيٍّ حِسانٍ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَفْرَفٍ فرش مرتفعة.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَعَبْقَرِيٍّ وطنافس.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٧٧-<span class="c5"> فَبِأَيِّ آلاءِ رَبِّكُما تُكَذِّبانِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَبِأَيِّ آلاءِ رَبِّكُما فبأى نعمة من نعم ربكما.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>تُكَذِّبانِ تجحدان أيها الثقلان.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٧٨-<span class="c5"> تَبارَكَ اسْمُ رَبِّكَ ذِي الْجَلالِ وَالْإِكْرامِ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>تَبارَكَ تعالى وتنزه.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>الْجَلالِ العظمة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَالْإِكْرامِ والإنعام.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>